name: Ushiwakamaru 牛若丸 / Fate/Grand Order
description:
weight 0.7~0.8 is best. (Different models may have different values for the weights.)

I created this LoRA as requested.

Please read the description.

outfit1 (stage2 ver)
hmushiwa, side ponytail, long hair, hat, tate eboshi, feather hair ornament, japanese armor, breast curtains, navel, detached sleeves, asymmetrical sleeves, white sleeves, purple sleeves, pom pom (clothes), tassel, blue panties, single glove, single pantsleg

outfit2
hmushiwa, side ponytail, long hair, single hair bun, single side bun, collarbone, swimsuit, blue bikini, open jacket, long sleeves, yellow jacket

outfit3
hmushiwa, side ponytail, long hair, single hair bun, single side bun, collarbone, swimsuit, blue bikini


I uploaded a sample image of the outfit as a post.

This was one of the hardest LoRAs I've ever created.
This is because she has a lot of asymmetrical hairstyles and outfits.

- Side ponytail
- Shoulder armor
- Breast curtains
- Sleeve colors
- Single pantsleg

There are a lot of asymmetrical elements, so it may not be possible to recreate it as perfectly as the original character.

Thank you.
